# Layout

Place Forge repos as **siblings** of the product project. Launchers default to `../<RepoName>`.

```text
parent/
  __PROJECT_ID__/          ← this product project
    scripts/*-mcp.sh
    .okf/
    .cursor/mcp.json       ← gitignored
  ForgeLifecycleContracts/
  ForgeRelay/
  ConceptForge/
  GovernanceForge/
  BuildForge/
  LaunchForge/             ← entry: mcp-server/dist/index.js
  OperateForge/
  CustomerForge/
  GrowthForge/
  RevenueForge/
  InsightForge/
  SunsetForge/
```

# Clone helper

From project root:

```bash
scripts/forge-clone-siblings.sh
```

Override org: `scripts/forge-clone-siblings.sh --org your-org`

# Overrides

When siblings are not peers, export per-server roots before starting MCP:

```bash
export LAUNCHFORGE_ROOT=/path/to/LaunchForge
export FORGERELAY_ROOT=/path/to/ForgeRelay
```

# Build requirement

Each sibling must be built before MCP start (`npm ci && npm run build`). Launchers fail fast with actionable messages when `dist/index.js` is missing.

